'''Grythsorin''' was the largest canyon system on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Ebra]]. It was also the location of [[lu-ramin]] [[Mining/Legends|mines]]. During the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] rule of Ebra, these mines were [[Prison/Legends|penal colonies]] worked by [[Ebranite]] political [[Prisoner/Legends|prisoners]].

